{"tid":1335872,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"好想死，著紅衫做冤魂","createTime":"2019-07-20T16:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T06:34:27.000Z","uid":280389,"like":8,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"941bce4997cd1d43aea0782e458009dddf577a55","tid":1335872,"uid":280389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"我是一位母親，六月開始情緒已低落，直到上星期日14/7發生極恐怖既黑警圍捕，心情已跌到谷底。每日不停哭，點可能會發生這種瘋癲狀態，警察完全失控，新城冇保安阻止，直到今天雙方就只有在拋波，此刻我真的很灰，好想死做隻冤魂每晚去找林鄭月娥、李家超、盧偉聰同鄭若譁，你哋班狗官係到做緊啲乜撚嘢。年輕人，老人家、陳伯及絕食者及一班媽媽都出來了，說出了訴求，但你們全部無動於終，還在死撐，係咪想有人被打死，為了香港人，我第一個願意站出來，因為我真的想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不停寃著你們直到全部死為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e9d5513c15164b0f268b54134c43b4cdb73f8b","tid":1335872,"uid":45772,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好死<br />\n1。藍絲會好開心<br />\n2。你有20%機會投胎做中國人"},{"pid":"216a74280b1d52981d6556dad5f7410be399f1e7","tid":1335872,"uid":261098,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"要死嗰個唔應該係你"},{"pid":"5bef6e3132dec3f0758a9c431ac752c508c36d07","tid":1335872,"uid":200083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千祈唔好死<br />\n1。藍絲會好開心<br />\n2。你有20%機會投胎做中國人</blockquote><br />\n第二一聽到就知慘過死"},{"pid":"b20c0e4bda16b78c420e2dc59da82b6e39d452a0","tid":1335872,"uid":79581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:47:42.000Z","msg":"唔好尋死 留有用之身 做冤魂呢件事未fact check"},{"pid":"867653b2bd1cb0ee6f90ac87f93759f6f1e7dc79","tid":1335872,"uid":302,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"cite